nited States of America flag on the mat, after they won a gold medal in the competition.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The video\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the United States\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"flag\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the caption, the TikTok user quipped about what the gymnasts may be thinking about when they do these impressive moves on the mat.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.155472355543214e-37, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnasts\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"these impressive moves\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You all think they are thinking of all their failed situationships during this??\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all their failed situationships\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the text over the video reads.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the text\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"the video reads\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee herself then responded to the fan's question in the comments, as she jokingly wrot