\": 1859, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, others disagreed with the joke about Olympians focusing on their failed relationships when competing.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the joke\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"their failed relationships\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think they are not.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think they are thinking of their love for their career & passion & goals, I think their exes are an afterthought!\\\"\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their love\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"their career\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"goals\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"their exes\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"an afterthought\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"one wrote.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think this helps them to NOT think about the failed situationships and that is why they are literally the best in the world,\\\" another added.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the failed situationships\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During their competition on July 30, Lee alsowent viral when fans spottedher and Biles sweetly talking about the TikTok videos they wanted to make.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": [{